pig-proof
Homonym Number:
Word Class:adjective
Sense Number: 1
Definition:[of fences and paddocks] capable of keeping out wild carnivore pigs [1800s & early 1900s.]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
